Kos chaotic: A kos rau hom Chaotic.
Deja Vu: Tib lub xeev mas peb tsiv nees.
Lub log ntev: Ua si ib Chaotic kev ua si nrog 20 xyaum.
Nrog kev pab me ntsis ntawm koj tus phooj ywg: yeej nyob rau hauv 3 tsiv.
Huv Slate: Rov mus pib xeev tom qab 5 tsiv.
Reversi: Yeej tus nraud style kev ua si.
Good Samaritan: Pab koj yeej nyob rau hauv 3 xyaum opponent.
Ob tug noog nrog ib pob zeb: yeej muaj kev ua si hauv ob lus cob qhia ib zaug.
Kev ua si qhov zoo nws: Chaw yuam winning khiav mus rau koj tus nrog sib ntaus.
Diav rawg hauv kev: yeej nyob rau ntau txoj kev uas ib tug nees.
Oops: Ua si ib unforced winning txav mus rau koj tus nrog sib ntaus.
Hauv hluav taws: Tej tawg vimchij hem ib yam ntawm koj tus kheej tej.
Opportunites tsis tau: Npeeg ua si ib winning tsiv.
Forced tes: Ua si ib hom ntau forced winning tsiv rau koj tus nrog sib ntaus.
